Detailed Description

Macros and types for use in the Xsens communication protocol and CMT classes.

This file contains useful macros for the Xsens CMT classes. These include Message Ids, sizes of messages, result/error codes, etc.

The macros and enumerators in this file are either used on multiple levels (XsensResultValue) or so numerous (CMT_MID_...) that it would not be justifiable to put them in a header file of a particular level.
